cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with the fine-grained recognition task, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed CoLA pipeline involves the use of 3D information, which suggests that robotics (cs.RO) could also be a relevant sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of scale-aware training and testing, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves segmentation, which is a common task in computer graphics (cs.GR).
